@node "Rel_notes" "Release notes"


@{b}Improvements and bug fixes.@{ub}

1. PREDATOR made 20-40% faster.

2. Bug fixed: with -a and -fFileName options  (predict  secondary structure
   for all sequences and write the results to the file  FileName)  only the
   last prediction appeared in  the  output  file  since  it  was  open for
   writing. Now it has been changed to appending  and  all  predictions are
   correctly output.

3. The executable for MS-DOS was corrupt and has been replaced.
@endnode

